item.title: Vidhya Apartment
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
2 bhk semi furnished flat is available for rent in Kasaba Bawada , near D.Y Patil college of Engineering and Technology,Kolhapur.
Property type : 2 bhk flat
Property size : 740 sq.Ft.
Expected rent (Rs): 7000/-
Construction year: 5 years
Floor no. : 2
Total floors :5
Number of bedrooms :2
A number of bath toilets :1
Parking : One four wheeler covered parking
Lift: Yes
Security : 24 hours security guard,
Amenities : Club house, indoor games with all ultra modern facilities. Kids park and garden area for senior citizens. Door video phone. Decorative entrance gate with security cabin, party lawn. Concrete roads with solar street lights eco lighting by using led lights. It is based in prime location which is accessible to schools, colleges, atm, restaurant, hospitals, market, etc
Water facility: Bore well, municipality water supply
